\"component list header, listed   ui-resizable\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h5><b>Lesson Summary</b></h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"DmlWZ\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list paragraph, listed   ui-resizable\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\" class=\"editable p-asset ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None\"><b>Below you will find a summary of the key content covered during the module:</b></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"ZSfPi\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list list-item, listed selected-class   border ui-resizable\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\" class=\"list-item editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None ng-touched\" spellcheck=\"false\"><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"\">Whistleblowing is the disclosure by organisation members of illegal, immoral or illegitimate practices to persons or organisations that may be able to effect action.</li><li class=\"\">Whistleblowing is essential in encouraging employees to bring ethical or legal violations to an internal authority so that action can be taken immediately</li><li class=\"\">By encouraging a whistleblowing culture, an organisation promotes transparent culture and clear communication.</li><li class=\"\">Whistleblowing carries the disadvantage of retaliatory investigations, charging the employee with minor offences and questioning their mental health.</li><li class=\"\">Whistleblowing policies and procedures should clearly explain the organisation's policies for handling whistleblowing, which can be communicated through training.</li><li class=\"\">Training should be offered at regular intervals to ensure it stays fresh in senior and junior management minds.</li><li class=\"\">Protection for whistleblowers in the UK is provided under the Public Interest Disclosure Act (PIDA) 1998, which amends the Employment Rights Act 1996.</li><li class=\"\">Under the FCA and PRA regulations, if a company is accused of wrongdoing, the FCA will scrutinise the companies policies and procedures closely.</li></ul></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li></ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-isolate-scope ui-sortable ng-not-empty\"><li id=\"jm8E0\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed   ui-resizable\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None ng-touched\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\" spellcheck=\"false\"><h1></h1><h5>Learning Outcomes</h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"cTWrp\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list paragraph, listed   ui-resizable\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\" class=\"editable p-asset ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty fontSmall None\"><b>Having completed this module you will be able to:</b></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"N9wut\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list list-item, listed   ui-resizable border\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\" class=\"list-item editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty fontSmall None ng-touched\" spellcheck=\"false\"><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"\">Identify the key components that facilitate whistleblowing programs</li><li class=\"\">List the different stages involved in a whistleblowing program</li><li class=\"\">Describe the role of different individuals both