 for employees to raise concerns.</li><li class=\"\">Training must cover three areas: How to raise a concern, how staff will be protected, and how the concern will be dealt with.</li><li class=\"\">Legal obligations fall into three categories: Disclosure, protection and protection.</li><li class=\"\">The reason why employees go to outside sources is that they become frustrated that their report was either ignored or that no action was taken by the company.</li></ul></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li></ul>\n"]}